metadata.name: Signs of the future
metadata.description:
Modern art, bright colors, abstract signs this style will decorate any room of the meta universe. 

This painting issued as a single, unique edition.

If you buy a NFT of 1 ETH, it is possible to send the original painting on canvas to the owner of the NFT.
